# Beads (issue tracker)
# - Track the task plan (`.beads/issues.jsonl`) in git so checkouts include the roadmap.
# - Ignore local runtime state (SQLite DB, daemon logs, etc).
/.beads/*
!/.beads/.gitignore
!/.beads/README.md
!/.beads/config.yaml
!/.beads/metadata.json
!/.beads/issues.jsonl
